WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.977
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.977 --> 00:00:04.360
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:05.840
I'm excited you're here.

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:07.840
I have some things on my heart to talk about.

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:14.148
I just wanted to point out what the Lord did whenever we had our prayer time yesterday.

00:00:14.148 --> 00:00:17.709
And you know, I never know what he's going to share.

00:00:17.709 --> 00:00:23.980
It's just amazing whenever you start praying and the Lord starts revealing things of the future to you.

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:29.555
Less than 24 hours later, Trump announces his mineral deal.

00:00:29.555 --> 00:00:40.686
And I told you all I saw President Trump—if you watch the prayer time—if you are skipping out on the prayer time just to hear me talk a little bit and not praying with us, you are missing out.

00:00:40.686 --> 00:00:47.920
I encourage you to listen to the whole video, especially if you like to intercede and pray for the nations.

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:55.039
I believe the Lord has called us to this YouTube channel; the primary focus is 'Prayer Changes Things.

00:00:55.039 --> 00:00:57.909
' And I believe we are changing things in nations.

00:00:58.217 --> 00:01:01.131
Yesterday, I feel like we went through the whole world.

00:01:01.131 --> 00:01:04.742
We were praying for elections and so many different things.

00:01:04.971 --> 00:01:11.680
The Lord had so many things on his heart that he wanted to talk about yesterday, obviously.

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:16.479
But one of the major things was that I saw President Trump coming in.

00:01:16.479 --> 00:01:18.391
He looked like Uncle Sam.

00:01:19.155 --> 00:01:37.295
His hair was like it always is, but he had a patriotic outfit on—a red and white pinstripe suit and a stars and stripes jacket, like an American flag-looking jacket, and he had a top hat on.

00:01:37.622 --> 00:01:44.457
He flew in on a jet plane—it looked like an F-16—into Ukraine in this vision.

00:01:48.216 --> 00:01:51.074
Whenever he got there, he started negotiating.

00:01:52.445 --> 00:01:57.484
I kept hearing in the spirit realm, 'The Art of the Deal, the Art of the Deal.

00:01:57.484 --> 00:02:04.369
' He was making a deal yesterday with Zelensky and the Ukrainian people.

00:02:09.848 --> 00:02:15.129
I'm just going to go over a little bit of it because there are many of you who do not watch the prayer time.

00:02:15.484 --> 00:02:19.874
He was making a deal, and I saw him negotiating.

00:02:20.331 --> 00:02:21.703
I saw minerals.

00:02:21.703 --> 00:02:25.314
I could see mounds of dirt in the background in this vision.

00:02:25.314 --> 00:02:37.359
I could see conveyor belts with the dirt moving, and then I could see fish coming from the ocean; they were flayed in half and looked like a fishing industry.

00:02:38.199 --> 00:02:47.783
The Lord showed me the fishing industry and then bales of wheat that were all wrapped in bundles with a white-looking cloth.

00:02:54.100 --> 00:02:54.330
They were the whole stems—the wheat grain and all of the stalks.

00:02:54.560 --> 00:03:07.577
The back end of the wheat was pointing this way, and the ends of it that were cut were pointing in a bundle toward France.

00:03:15.530 --> 00:03:20.987
I could see it pointing toward France, laying down.

00:03:22.267 --> 00:03:35.820
The Lord was focusing my attention in the vision; I could see the round base of the stalks of the wheat wrapped in a bundle.

00:03:37.710 --> 00:03:44.274
He said, 'Brandon, this is in play as you speak right now.

00:03:44.274 --> 00:03:46.307
This is about to manifest.

00:03:46.307 --> 00:03:53.640
' I could hear it echoing inside of me that this major mineral deal was about to take place.

00:03:54.140 --> 00:04:08.974
Lo and behold, 24 hours later—after we uploaded that video that morning—they announced on the news that they had signed the mineral deal.

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:15.794
So, we saw a prophetic word that was a 24-hour turnaround.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:31.816
That was a big deal to me because usually I wait months, or years sometimes, to see something, but I know there was an urgency to what we were praying over last night and interceding that this would get done—that this was a major domino.

00:04:31.816 --> 00:04:44.057
Then I saw Vladimir Putin with North Korea in the background with Xi Jinping and his allies.

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:50.663
Vladimir Putin had a hand of red and white playing cards.

00:04:58.740 --> 00:05:02.049
He had five cards in his hand.

00:05:03.210 --> 00:05:12.839
They were big playing cards, and he was holding them out like a fan and hiding behind those cards, watching to see what was happening in Ukraine.

00:05:20.739 --> 00:05:28.994
I saw the words 'World War III' in black letters across.

00:05:29.389 --> 00:05:34.464
Then I remember the oil derrick—I think that was over the Mediterranean.

00:05:34.464 --> 00:05:37.823
Yes, because there were so many things the Lord showed us yesterday, folks.

00:05:37.823 --> 00:05:39.126
It was really interesting.

00:05:39.126 --> 00:05:47.119
Then the Lord showed me Germany, France, and then NATO.

00:05:47.626 --> 00:05:49.813
I saw an alliance.

00:05:53.280 --> 00:06:03.410
I saw the land where Russia has taken over; I saw them taking control permanently over that land, trying to create a peace agreement within a four-year window.

00:06:05.210 --> 00:06:10.280
I saw a time span waiting behind those cards.

00:06:23.190 --> 00:06:34.032
But I heard the old USSR, the old Soviet Union, was with the KGB, and it was like roots inside Putin; he wants the whole thing, and he was looking for Kyiv.

00:06:39.290 --> 00:06:39.635
He wants the whole Ukraine.

00:06:45.725 --> 00:06:50.188
They were waiting for Trump to get out of the way.

00:06:50.188 --> 00:06:55.005
He has a plan, and in this plan, it was more evil.

00:06:55.268 --> 00:06:57.245
I could see the escalation of war.

00:06:59.279 --> 00:07:07.540
He was watching behind his playing cards, trying to play poker.

00:07:14.794 --> 00:07:15.740
A poker face.

00:07:21.103 --> 00:07:29.618
I saw North Korea siding with China as an Asian front in the days ahead, using Korea as a lynchpin.

00:07:38.600 --> 00:07:44.194
Eventually, I believe Kim Jong-un will be removed, and through his sister, there will be revival.

00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:56.467
I saw riots starting to take place in China—which we see in the news now—but I saw riots becoming more mainstream despite efforts to hush them down.

00:07:58.160 --> 00:08:14.279
Then it started to spread to other nations, like Canada, because of things that will be decided in the future that will be more suppressive, shutting up freedom of speech.

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:26.993
It will be more of a lockdown because of the way they think versus the way Christians think—great persecution coming to the Christians.

00:08:26.993 --> 00:08:29.531
Now, we got the emails.

00:08:32.346 --> 00:08:39.128
I don't mean to upset you all, but I have to speak what the Lord tells me to say regardless.

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:41.199
It's not easy for me.

00:08:52.160 --> 00:08:56.896
I'm going to be real with you.

00:08:56.896 --> 00:09:05.839
It's very hard to come on here and tell you these words when I know it's going to upset people.

00:09:05.839 --> 00:09:09.235
Jeremiah had to do the same thing.

00:09:11.657 --> 00:09:15.565
I know your heart, and I know my job is not to scare you but to prepare you.

00:09:16.251 --> 00:09:27.980
I want to prepare you and sound the alarm as loud as I can for what the Spirit of the Lord is telling me to say, for I am accountable to him only, not to you.

00:09:27.980 --> 00:09:33.700
Now you say, 'Well, Brandon, I don't agree with you.

00:09:33.700 --> 00:09:36.107
' That's fine.

00:09:36.107 --> 00:09:45.591
Do you know how many millions of people—literally, I would say probably 10,000 a month at least—say something because they don't agree with me?

00:09:45.591 --> 00:09:50.549
They are more vocal than a lot of you are with the nasty emails.

00:09:50.549 --> 00:09:52.423
But you know what?

00:09:52.423 --> 00:09:55.519
I keep going because God said to.

00:09:55.519 --> 00:09:59.180
Persecution comes for the word's sake.

00:09:59.180 --> 00:10:01.279
You say I've missed it.

00:10:01.279 --> 00:10:02.171
That's fine.

00:10:02.171 --> 00:10:03.063
Keep watching.

00:10:03.063 --> 00:10:19.876
You say you hear this prophet so-and-so saying this, and they say good things are coming to Canada and that there's going to be a flipping of the boat—that it's going to be uncovered just like it was in 2020.

00:10:19.876 --> 00:10:35.600
Folks, the prophets—I'm going to be just real bold with you right now—the prophetic people who spoke and told you that Joe Biden was going to be removed and that President Trump and all the prophetic words and everything that was spoken in 2020 were false prophecies.

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:36.520
They missed it.

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:43.084
But a lot of them didn't have the guts to come on and say, "We missed it.

00:10:43.084 --> 00:10:48.951
" Instead, they kept kicking it down, going with QAnon and all the things they said.

00:10:49.410 --> 00:10:57.480
I'm not here to pick or poke at anybody; I'm here to tell you and shed light on things.

00:10:57.480 --> 00:11:05.748
If I miss it, I'm very quick to come on here and say, "Listen, I missed it.

00:11:05.748 --> 00:11:08.091
" I don't have anything to hide from you.

00:11:08.091 --> 00:11:12.902
I don't answer to you; I answer to Him.

00:11:19.189 --> 00:11:28.079
And if I get in the flesh and I hear something off, then by my goodness, I want to say, "God, correct me, but make me stronger and make me sharper to hear You in these end times.

00:11:28.079 --> 00:11:29.400
" I'm not ashamed.

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:43.519
People pick at you all the time, but I'm telling you: I believe there are a lot of people telling you sugar-coated words about what is coming to Canada in the days ahead.

00:11:45.330 --> 00:11:49.793
There will be a very big shaking in Canada—so much so that I saw an economic disaster.

00:11:49.793 --> 00:11:57.920
As you see these birthing pains in America, the window of opportunity the Lord is giving us right now for the digital platform, we're seeing that all coming about.

00:11:57.920 --> 00:12:05.419
And Eric Trump made an announcement about the banks and about the digital currency.

00:12:06.800 --> 00:12:08.126
There's so much going on right now.

00:12:08.126 --> 00:12:11.566
Trump is saying that he wants to eliminate the IRS.

00:12:15.919 --> 00:12:25.520
What did I warn you about the IRS and the Iraqi dinar—about people not paying their taxes or doing what they're supposed to do because they get the sense that the IRS is going to be done away with?

00:12:25.520 --> 00:12:31.240
But the Lord showed me there was a warning to that.

00:12:31.630 --> 00:12:34.862
Now, if you don't want to listen, don't listen.

00:12:34.862 --> 00:12:46.880
There's something there that's a catch; there's something there the Holy Spirit is trying to warn us about.

00:12:46.880 --> 00:12:56.280
This is way before everybody was saying that anyone making below $200,000 is not going to have to pay taxes.

00:12:56.280 --> 00:12:58.942
There's something more to this.

00:12:58.942 --> 00:13:09.973
Why is the Lord warning me to tell you this way before they even started talking about this stuff?

00:13:10.240 --> 00:13:13.191
And I'm like, "Okay, God, what are You saying in this?

00:13:21.149 --> 00:13:21.491
What are You saying about what President Trump is saying?

00:13:21.833 --> 00:13:31.453
What more is there to this, and why would You warn me about this?

00:13:31.453 --> 00:13:43.760
" So, going back to the vision from last night, we see all these things taking place.

00:13:43.760 --> 00:13:48.920
We see President Trump coming in now.

00:13:54.630 --> 00:13:57.623
I saw him on an eagle, and he was flying out; he left on an eagle.

00:13:57.623 --> 00:14:08.674
Then I saw negotiations with Israel and Hamas and what's going on with Gaza.

00:14:17.973 --> 00:14:20.906
I saw, not a two-state solution, but the Temple being discussed—a peace treaty so that they could build the Temple Mount.

00:14:20.906 --> 00:14:35.154
Then I saw major oil across the Mediterranean with an oil derrick dripping, meaning there is a lot of oil.

00:14:40.440 --> 00:14:42.209
The Lord warned me about the oil, and that was part of the vision I had last night.

00:14:42.209 --> 00:14:52.360
Then I saw the Middle East as a whole, and what I saw was Iraq rising from the ashes.

00:14:52.360 --> 00:15:01.220
I saw new buildings and beautiful structures coming to Iraq: skyscrapers, shopping malls, and all kinds of new housing developments.

00:15:01.220 --> 00:15:03.074
Beautiful things.

00:15:03.074 --> 00:15:08.480
An economic boom is about to take place in Iraq.

00:15:24.497 --> 00:15:24.915
A major flow of finances is coming to Iraq—huge money.

00:15:24.915 --> 00:15:33.431
When I saw this, it was just like what's going on in Saudi Arabia.

00:15:41.072 --> 00:15:41.264
I saw the economics shift from China and America to Iraq and the Middle East.

00:15:44.533 --> 00:15:45.399
The Middle East becomes the breadbasket of the world financially.

00:15:46.508 --> 00:15:53.919
The Lord said to me, "The beginning stages of the Antichrist are at hand.

00:16:16.272 --> 00:16:16.824
" A superpower will rise out of all this as an economic hero—an economic hero, when all of the world's economies are crashing all around.

00:16:16.824 --> 00:16:31.920
If you look at what the princes and the head people in Saudi Arabia—these rich billionaire men, these tycoon guys—they're all saying, "We're going digital; we want to sell, buy, and trade in these cryptocurrencies.

00:16:31.920 --> 00:16:34.906
" I've seen this stuff; people are sending me things.

00:16:34.906 --> 00:16:37.336
Look, it's all pointing to the Middle East.

00:16:37.336 --> 00:16:50.628
So, as we see the Middle East rise up and start to become this super world power with Saudi Arabia, this is what's going to happen.

00:16:50.628 --> 00:16:54.811
I've told you who I believe the Antichrist is.

00:16:54.811 --> 00:17:06.510
We're seeing that he will play a major part in the days ahead with the temple agreement with Israel.

00:17:06.510 --> 00:17:15.062
Israel is part of the Middle East, and we will see Israel rise as the blessing of Abraham.

00:17:15.062 --> 00:17:17.520
God said, "Remember what I told you all?

00:17:20.125 --> 00:17:32.223
I'm going to breathe on the Abrahamic covenant, showing the world that I am still the God over Israel, that He is the I AM THAT I AM.

00:17:33.817 --> 00:17:39.500
" And I'm telling you: He's going to show up and show off to the Israeli people.

00:17:39.500 --> 00:17:43.152
Watch what happens in the days ahead.

00:17:51.377 --> 00:17:51.679
I saw fruit the size of baseballs—massive fruit, massive agriculture, prosperity over their land like you wouldn't believe.

00:17:51.679 --> 00:17:57.386
Now, you might say, "Well, I'm not for Benjamin Netanyahu; I'm not for Benjamin Netanyahu.

00:17:57.386 --> 00:18:03.776
I think he's evil because of what he did to the Palestinians and all this stuff.

00:18:04.320 --> 00:18:11.947
" It has nothing to do with a leader; it has nothing to do with the head of the government.

00:18:11.947 --> 00:18:16.781
This has to do with a covenant that was made with a people.

00:18:24.693 --> 00:18:24.960
I want to say that again: it has nothing to do with the Israeli government.

00:18:28.160 --> 00:18:33.400
You can disagree or agree with what they've done over there, but it's about the bloodline and the Jewish people.

00:18:33.400 --> 00:18:36.994
It has nothing to do with politics.

00:18:36.994 --> 00:18:42.231
It has to do with a covenant made thousands of years ago.

00:18:46.853 --> 00:18:55.863
God is still acknowledging and holding true to the covenant He made with Abraham, saying, "I'm going to make you the father of many nations; I'm going to bless you for a thousand generations.

00:19:09.180 --> 00:19:09.610
" What I'm telling you is it has nothing to do with Benjamin Netanyahu or the politics of Israel today.

00:19:09.610 --> 00:19:24.000
Politics can change overnight, but what never changes is the Word of God and what He said He would do for His people, saying, "I stand by the covenant I made with Abraham.

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:31.188
" God is a God whose yeses are yeses and whose nos are nos.

00:19:43.896 --> 00:19:44.233
He doesn't falter or move away from what He said He would do.

00:19:47.394 --> 00:19:56.891
So, you need to know it has nothing to do with politics; it has everything to do with a covenant that God made.

00:19:56.891 --> 00:20:05.697
He is not going to change His mind about a covenant He made because He is a God who does not lie.

00:20:05.697 --> 00:20:08.600
Does that make sense to you all?

00:20:08.600 --> 00:20:12.200
Somebody needs to shout, "Amen," at that!

00:20:12.200 --> 00:20:15.752
I'm telling you, there is a covenant.

00:20:15.752 --> 00:20:27.662
God has a covenant with you and me, the very covenant He made with every single one of you as you are adopted into Him by grace.

00:20:32.137 --> 00:20:46.560
You are saved through faith as we turn ourselves from our sin and humble ourselves before a God who loves us and say, "God, I need You more than anything going on around me.

00:20:55.988 --> 00:20:56.354
I need a God who will love me and take over my life.

00:20:57.710 --> 00:20:59.030
I surrender myself over to You.

00:21:01.919 --> 00:21:02.195
" And guess what happens?

00:21:02.195 --> 00:21:09.816
That covenant He made with His Son's blood on that cross—He took it all for you.

00:21:09.816 --> 00:21:14.149
He made a covenant the moment you take it.

00:21:21.027 --> 00:21:21.653
This is covenant.

00:21:30.503 --> 00:21:30.880
This communion cup is covenant.

00:21:30.880 --> 00:21:32.160
Do you understand?

00:21:32.160 --> 00:21:39.257
This is a covenant that what I took on my body, you don't need to have in your body.

00:21:39.257 --> 00:21:44.799
What I did for you, you don't have to live in poverty.

00:21:49.599 --> 00:21:50.079
I became poor that you might be rich.

00:21:53.790 --> 00:21:53.940
I became sick that you might be healed.

00:21:57.395 --> 00:22:00.840
I became everything that the devil has thrown at you since the beginning of time, since Adam fell.

00:22:00.840 --> 00:22:09.102
Everything from mental torments to broken marriages, I took it all so you could have prosperity in the spirit realm.

00:22:09.102 --> 00:22:09.943
That's covenant.

00:22:09.943 --> 00:22:11.269
That's covenant talk.

00:22:11.269 --> 00:22:12.560
This is covenant.

00:22:12.560 --> 00:22:17.039
He said, "Do it often in remembrance of me.

00:22:17.039 --> 00:22:26.799
" So the same covenant that was is still strong today for the Jewish people because they don't recognize Jesus yet.

00:22:26.799 --> 00:22:27.496
They don't.

00:22:27.496 --> 00:22:30.560
But God is a God of his word.

00:22:30.560 --> 00:22:35.351
So we see the blessing on what I'm telling you.

00:22:35.351 --> 00:22:42.275
We see a blessing coming on the oil, and we're going to see it coming out of the Mediterranean.

00:22:42.275 --> 00:22:44.989
We're going to see it.

00:22:44.989 --> 00:22:51.920
But as we see the Mahdi rise up, he will not rise up as poor.

00:22:51.920 --> 00:22:55.600
He will not rise up as weak.

00:22:55.600 --> 00:22:59.440
He's going to rise up as the world's superpower.

00:23:02.594 --> 00:23:15.080
And the Lord spoke to me yesterday and he said, "Brandon, you are about to see the bread basket of the world—that first Babylon that fell—and now you will see Babylon rise again.

00:23:25.919 --> 00:23:26.519
A major economic turnaround is coming to Iraq.

00:23:31.370 --> 00:23:31.740
" And I saw brand new palm trees.

00:23:31.740 --> 00:23:34.613
I saw it all, ladies and gentlemen.

00:23:42.020 --> 00:23:42.730
And I saw wealth coming to the Middle East.

00:24:01.143 --> 00:24:01.600
And as we see that, we know that this is the beginning of the true beginning.

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:13.780
He said, "Everything started in the Middle East with the Garden of Eden, and now it will end in the Middle East with the end of ends, the end times.

00:24:13.780 --> 00:24:17.120
" The Jewish people—watch what God does in these days ahead.

00:24:17.120 --> 00:24:36.502
So, I saw a deal being cut with a peace agreement in the days ahead with Trump, and the Prince of Saudi Arabia will be a big puppet master in this.

00:24:36.502 --> 00:24:39.075
And folks, we're seeing it.

00:24:39.848 --> 00:24:41.867
So, we're going to see the window.

00:24:51.051 --> 00:24:51.383
I believe it.

00:24:51.383 --> 00:24:55.379
So, thank you for joining me with my recap.

00:24:55.379 --> 00:25:01.770
I just thought of what the Lord was showing us and what we see in the news today.

00:25:01.770 --> 00:25:09.863
When Eric Trump said all that he said, we see that everybody's calling for a global recession; most believe it could be worse than a depression.

00:25:09.863 --> 00:25:17.154
I truly believe that for the body of Christ, the best is yet to come.

00:25:20.539 --> 00:25:30.420
And that's why I tried to explain to you yesterday when the Lord says to Diana and me and Braden, "Days of great fun are coming for y'all.

00:25:30.420 --> 00:25:34.799
" I truly want you to understand what fun is to us.

00:25:40.284 --> 00:25:58.794
And that's why I said that for the first time yesterday: what's fun to us is seeing the lost saved, casting out devils, laying hands on the sick, seeing blinded eyes open, having ears that can't hear, hear, raising the dead—doing all the things that the Great Commission told us to do when Jesus said, "Go into all the world.

00:25:58.794 --> 00:26:02.760
" That's what's fun to us, isn't it, baby?

00:26:02.760 --> 00:26:03.950
We're excited.

00:26:03.950 --> 00:26:07.406
That's what fun is to us.

00:26:07.406 --> 00:26:16.650
Now, most people say, "Well, fun to me is going shopping in Beverly Hills.

00:26:16.650 --> 00:26:26.102
" My fun is I want to see a million people saved in a day.

00:26:26.102 --> 00:26:42.913
My fun is I want to see a whole row of wheelchairs in front of a platform, everyone stand up at once and go, "Boop!

00:27:00.663 --> 00:27:00.960
I'm healed.

00:27:00.960 --> 00:27:04.297
I've been in a wheelchair my whole life.

00:27:11.240 --> 00:27:11.520
I was quadriplegic.

00:27:11.520 --> 00:27:13.451
Boop, I got healed.

00:27:25.006 --> 00:27:32.747
" That is going to be the day that I'm looking forward to.

00:27:32.747 --> 00:27:39.639
And I believe we're right on the cusp of it.

00:27:39.639 --> 00:27:46.365
The greatest move of God that this world has ever seen is about to pour out on this earth like we've never seen before.

00:27:46.365 --> 00:27:49.931
Judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:27:54.497 --> 00:27:55.279
And as we see things shaking, as we see things changing, we are seeing new voices.

00:27:55.279 --> 00:28:04.754
